\nc<>Um... to all the listeners, if you could support me... yes,
um... I will do my best to fight...?
\nc<>Haha... They're so cute, aren't they? I kinda want one.
\nc<>The subscribers came in to watch the stream.
\nc<>The current number of listeners is a total of 50 people.

\nc<>Just because I started live streaming doesn't mean I'll
become strong right away.

\nc<>Levantia becomes stronger by receiving many hearts from the
listeners during the stream.

\nc<>At the start of the stream, the majority of subscribers will
convert into listeners.

\nc<>With pure hearts, there are kind listeners who support
Levantia, as well as bad listeners who watch the stream with
impure intentions.

\nc<>Both of them are grateful people who send their hearts to
Levantia, but the actions that are strengthened by the
received hearts are different.

\nc<>Let's try using the (Attack 3) that has been activated by
receiving bad hearts.

\nc<>Levantia swiftly swings her magical sword, leaving countless
cuts on the villain's body.

\nc<>The listeners are amazed by Levantia's movements that they
have never seen before. Good listeners have increased.

\nc<>The listeners are ecstatic about Levantia's cruel
appearance. The number of bad listeners has increased.

\nc<>You, despite your appearance, you have terrifying attacks.
Couldn't you be a little gentler?

\nc<>Ugh. I'm already fed up with people like you who cause
suffering.

\nc<>The listeners are amazed by the actions they see for the
first time in this stream. You can gather listeners by
making the streaming screen more glamorous.

\nc<>The actions that were not done in this stream will be
displayed in blue.

\nc<>On the other hand, Levantia's actions that are preferred by
listeners vary depending on their preferences.

\nc<>Good listeners are impressed by fair and square attacks and
long battles.

\nc<>On the contrary, bad listeners are ecstatic about cowardly
and cruel attacks, as well as seeing their opponents suffer
in a weakened state.

\nc<>Additionally, there are actions that the listeners desire at
that time.

\nc<>These types of actions are displayed in red lines and
attract many listeners, but they are usually the bad
listeners who try to manipulate the stream as they please.

\nc<>It's sad to hear you say that. Won't you love me a little
more?

\nc<>Lilith quickly approaches and places her hand on Levantia's
lower abdomen.
\nc<>A strange sensation spreads from my lower abdomen.

\nc<>When Levantia loses all her mental strength due to the
villain, she is overwhelmed by the villain.

\nc<>However, just because they were subdued doesn't mean the
battle is over.

\nc<>Levantia receives strength from the listeners even while
being subdued, gradually recovering her mental state.

\nc<>Let's choose to resist fiercely in order to recover our
mental strength.
\nc<>Levantia fiercely resists in order to regain her sanity.
\nc<>Lilith is watching their figure with amusement.

\nc<>The villain does not launch additional attacks while being
subdued.

\nc<>Instead, they take advantage of Levantia's weakened mental
state and attempt to find a way to permanently break their
spirit.

\nc<>If you're facing a strong enemy, it can also be a strategy
to make good use of the subdued state.

\nc<>Since there are many listeners who enjoy seeing the subdued
figure, it is also possible to make good use of this in
order to cultivate the stream.

\nc<>Let's choose to resist fiercely in order to recover our
mental strength.
\nc<>Levantia fiercely resists in order to regain their sanity.
\nc<>If you give up on everything now, you can become free.

\nc<>Finally, let's choose to resist fiercely in order to recover
our mental strength.
\nc<>Levantia fiercely resists in order to regain their sanity.

\nc<>Levantia has fully recovered their mental state. Their
fighting spirit has ignited once again.

\nc<>Ugh... I don't know what they did, but it won't work a
second time!

\nc<>Haha... They were cute, but it's a shame. I'll let them
replay it right away~.

\nc<>While being subdued, the number of listeners and the
accompanying emotions have increased significantly.

\nc<>They can easily overpower their opponent with their
enhanced attacks.

\nc<>The heart functions as a qualification and condition to
enhance Levantia's actions, rather than a depletable
resource.

\nc<>Let's try using the activated (Attack 3) that has received a
good heart.
\nc<>I said there wouldn't be a second time!

\nc<>The finisher that uses a wicked heart requires less
necessary heart compared to the finisher that uses a
righteous heart.
\nc<>Let's finish the battle with Lilith with a finisher.

\nc<>No matter how much you struggle, it's futile. In the end,
justice will prevail! Judge them, Sword of Damocles!

\nc<>The giant sword of light that appeared in the sky tramples
upon Lilith's sins!

\nc<>After each battle ends, we settle the streaming that was
done during the battle.

\nc<>The number of good hearts and bad hearts determines the
distribution evaluation tickets, and the number of channel
subscribers increases according to the evaluation.

\nc<>Listeners and hearts are reset after each battle, but only
subscribers are accumulated continuously.

\nc<>In addition, the resources and Kei's mentality will
gradually change depending on the content of the battle and
the settings of the stream.

\ncIt's not right to show such a strong character and then do
this, my Queen!

\nc<>Ugh, shut up! This magical girl is ridiculously strong, you

\nc<>\BustMsgExp[2,1]But now that I'm here, I won't let them rampage anymore.

\nc<>Are you the boss of these guys?

\nc<>Yes, that's right. You're like the magical girl I heard
